            <li>Portfolio - <a href="https://soudev.netlify.app" target="_blank">Click here</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p>If you want to help the project so that we can pay for the hosting:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>BTC - 1AXtxAo6RWpyXLzt5tzU7hRUAmce3rgmrp</li>
            <li>BCH - qrl7unl97v5p5k3cwm9erchk8wtghzt7vg2l8q4egn</li>
            <li>LTC - LQ2WLDJC1uW6wqutHDGhFwbbA8rDxMrFZp</li>
            <li>DOGE - D9BUz7DXrjM6UAm8ef9u7j5jW2ymhXLR5o</li>
            <li>TRX - TNfVVQEjnNz382XBEETXajPvZUsTS8FqAP</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <script src="javascripts/index.js"></script>
    <script src="javascripts/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
